"```sql\nSELECT CONCAT(forename, ' ', surname) AS name, \n       YEAR(CURRENT_TIMESTAMP) - YEAR(dob) AS age\nFROM drivers\nWHERE nationality = 'Japanese'\nORDER BY dob DESC\nLIMIT 1;\n```\n\nThis SQL query selects the full name and age of the youngest Japanese driver by filtering the `drivers` table for those with a nationality of 'Japanese', ordering by date of birth in descending order (so the youngest is first), and limiting the result to the top entry."